    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "きゃあ！",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 0.8
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1106.6666881,
          "startTime": 1.9066666881
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "いたたたた……まさかワープして空中に出るなんて……\nでも、無事に戻って来られたみたいね",
      "startTime": 7.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "あら？　{user}さんがいない\nまさか、途中ではぐれたの！？",
      "startTime": 13.6875222484,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "こ、ここにいます……",
      "startTime": 16.5974378546,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、私の下から声が？\nあ、私の下敷きに……",
      "startTime": 22.9521538179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "下敷き？\nじゃあ、俺の上に乗っている、この柔らかい感触は……",
      "startTime": 27.5666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hug-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4390.5897894,
          "startTime": 30.0333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hug-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5757.256456,
          "startTime": 31.3999999999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "きゃああああ！　どこ触ってるのよ！\nいつまでもくっついていないで、さっさと離れなさい！",
      "startTime": 35.4604990167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ララ達が元の世界に帰って、数日後",
      "startTime": 40.3769389989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、これはいい写真ね\nララに送ってあげたいくらいだわ",
      "startTime": 45.8271658105,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2493.557729000003,
          "startTime": 45.1704991438
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん？　何を見ているんですか？",
      "startTime": 48.2838119549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "この間のクリスマスイベントの記事よ\nゲスト出演したララ達のことが書かれているの",
      "startTime": 54.2016783318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、これを見て\n私とララがステージでMCをしている時の写真よ",
      "startTime": 59.1683448714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "よく撮れていますね。でも、この写真の莉央さん……\nもしかして、恥ずかしがっていますか？",
      "startTime": 70.0999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "だって、仕方ないじゃない。中が水着とはいえ\nこんなに短いスカートじゃ、恥ずかしくもなるわよ",
      "startTime": 77.5283408485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、寮で俺に衣装を見せた時は\n照れていませんでしたよね？",
      "startTime": 84.2333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "貴方は特別よ。マネージャーに見られて、いちいち\n恥ずかしがっていたらアイドルなんて務まらないでしょ",
      "startTime": 90.2791536095,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "でも、ステージで大勢の視線を意識したら\n緊張して、なんだか恥ずかしく思えてきちゃって……",
      "startTime": 97.9458263797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "あの状況でも物怖じしないララは\n本当にアイドルが向いているかもしれないわね",
      "startTime": 105.1124925377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんも歌っている時は堂々としてたじゃないですか\nステージの莉央さんは格好良かったですよ",
      "startTime": 112.1666659038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "素人のララ達があんなに頑張ったんだもの\nプロの私が情けないところは見せられないわよ",
      "startTime": 118.4951310955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "衣装のおかげもあって、ライブは凄く盛り上がったわね",
      "startTime": 123.9113248231,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "会場の熱気に押されて、みんなもいつも以上の\nパフォーマンスを発揮出来たんじゃないかしら",
      "startTime": 131.328459724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "おかげでワープに必要なエネルギーも十分集まって\nララ達は無事に旅立つことが出来たわ",
      "startTime": 137.6951248648,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、元いた世界にちゃんと辿り着けたかしら\n私達みたいに変な場所に飛ばされていないといいけど",
      "startTime": 145.0617915315,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、あの発明品はエネルギー不足だったのに\nどうして俺達の時は動いたんでしょう",
      "startTime": 153.6333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "ララの話だと、予期しないエネルギーの注入があって\n機械が誤作動を起こしたらしいけど……",
      "startTime": 160.6092971089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "エネルギーを入れた覚えはないし、そもそも動かせる\nだけのエネルギーなんてどこにもなかったはずよ",
      "startTime": 167.3759637756,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "エネルギー……。そういえば、あの時\n莉央さんは改造した衣装を着ていましたよね？",
      "startTime": 175.0333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ。人の『想い』が生み出すエネルギーを\n回収出来るように改造した衣装を……",
      "startTime": 181.5955628398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "まさか、私の『想い』がエネルギーを生み出していた？\nそれが衣装を通じて機械に流れ込んだ？",
      "startTime": 189.8559821352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "だとしたら、あの時の私はエネルギーを生み出すほど\n強い感情を抱いていたってこと？",
      "startTime": 198.7622295065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-rio023.m4a",
      "text": "あの時は確か、私は貴方と\nララのことについて話していて……",
      "startTime": 205.0955628398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-rio024.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが、ララのような\n素直で可愛い子が好きだと言うのを聞いて、私は……",
      "startTime": 210.0288961731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_13_03-rio025.m4a",
      "text": "強い想いがエネルギーになる……強い感情が……\n感情……もしかして、あの時私は……やきも……",
      "startTime": 221.4288961731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
